data.description: *Professional photos to be uploaded Friday evening* Welcome to this stunning, updated home nestled in the highly desired Blooms Crossing Community of Manassas Park. Meticulously renovated, this residence boasts new flooring and fresh paint throughout, creating a bright, inviting space. The main level greets you with an open concept layout, featuring new LVP flooring and a gourmet kitchen adorned with updated granite countertops and stainless steel appliances that overlooks the cozy family room. French doors lead to a spacious deck and a private fenced backyard, ideal for entertaining or relaxation. Upstairs, the primary bedroom offers a luxurious retreat with a spa-inspired en suite bathroom boasting dual vanities, a walk-in shower, and a soaking tub. Three additional bedrooms and a second full bath complete the upper level. The lower level impresses with a stylishly tiled floor, a built-in bar, and a newly constructed bonus room with closet, accompanied by a third full bathroom - perfect for hosting guests. Added conveniences include a lower-level laundry area with brand new washer and dryer. Other notable features include  new roof and windows in 2018. Enjoy not only the home's features but also the community amenities, close proximity to shopping, schools, restaurants, VRE, and major transportation routes such as Rt. 28 and 234.
